<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="273" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,150,1292]" pageId="16" pageNumber="273">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1230,1256]" pageId="16" pageNumber="273">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[860,999,1230,1256]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="273">microdontus</emphasis>
, referring to the two ventroapical denticles of the valva.
</paragraph>
